    "name": "Light Up the Dark",
    "steam_appid": 3040850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Light Up the Dark》是一款设定在黑暗世界中的殖民生存模拟游戏，途中充满未知的恐惧。收集资源、建造设施、自动化流程、研发科技并探索随机生成的地图。管理三种不同类型的殖民者，保持他们的理性，或是利用他们的疯狂。以自己独有的方式解决无尽而有趣的挑战，开辟属于你的生存之路。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >黑暗中的生存挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片被黑暗笼罩的世界里，没有任何自然光源。长时间处于黑暗之中意味着死亡。为了生存，你必须建造人造光源，并不断收集资源以维持光源运行。不断研发新的科技、升级现有光源，或创新出更强大的照明设施，驱散黑暗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/131131b10f3bed894c684a636a3a9473.poster.avif?t=1767702012\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/131131b10f3bed894c684a636a3a9473.webm?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/131131b10f3bed894c684a636a3a9473.mp4?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深层而复杂的天赋系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >殖民者的经历将塑造他们的能力。生活方式、日常习惯，亦或是那些欣喜若狂或悲伤至极的时刻，都会让他们得到不同的特质。这些特质可能是祝福，也可能是诅咒，这往往取决于不同的视点——当然，也并非总是如此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/047dd2247d13919eebf98e0548f20d53.poster.avif?t=1767702012\" width=800 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/047dd2247d13919eebf98e0548f20d53.webm?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/047dd2247d13919eebf98e0548f20d53.mp4?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理三种各司其职的殖民者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >殖民者分为三类：劳工、巧匠和玄师。他们拥有不同的技能、优势、弱点和偏好。你需要设法让他们和谐共存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/7721f99ca7c6a73a6264a51933489157.poster.avif?t=1767702012\" width=800 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/7721f99ca7c6a73a6264a51933489157.webm?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/7721f99ca7c6a73a6264a51933489157.mp4?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的挑战 vs 多样的解法</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的资源：</strong>大量的资源等著您去收集、生产或消耗。你可以利用多种技能来加工资源，例如采矿、手工、耕作、畜牧、炼金、工程，以及利用蒸气、燃烧、地热和电力等多种能源。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/a964f23ec2cac7fd512569da0a39d537.poster.avif?t=1767702012\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/a964f23ec2cac7fd512569da0a39d537.webm?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/a964f23ec2cac7fd512569da0a39d537.mp4?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>先进的物流：</strong>利用诸如自动机械、飞艇与传送门等先进科技来改善你的物流网路，提高效率。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/5bdf0652c41c19d6cc575e2044fd80ea.poster.avif?t=1767702012\" width=800 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/5bdf0652c41c19d6cc575e2044fd80ea.webm?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/5bdf0652c41c19d6cc575e2044fd80ea.mp4?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗之力：</strong>尝试驾驭环绕在基地周围、压抑而致命的黑暗本质——虚空的力量。只是代价可能极为沉重。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/147b637ddee31aa8572a5e5438bb0e94.poster.avif?t=1767702012\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/147b637ddee31aa8572a5e5438bb0e94.webm?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/147b637ddee31aa8572a5e5438bb0e94.mp4?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>疯狂机制：</strong>你需要制定策略来面对精神失常的殖民者，尤其是对于极度危险的疯狂罪犯。你可以将他们囚禁、尝试进行高风险的治疗，或者放任他们四处游荡，任其纵火、谋杀、自杀、或是露体。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/be6c1c2cf8f8f02626e200a8bf84601a.poster.avif?t=1767702012\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/be6c1c2cf8f8f02626e200a8bf84601a.webm?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040850/extras/be6c1c2cf8f8f02626e200a8bf84601a.mp4?t=1767702012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高度重玩性：</strong>用自己的方式来进行游戏。你可以选择不同的策略、游戏风格，甚至可以进行角色扮演。结合随机生成的地图和複杂的游戏机制，这是一款极具重玩价值的游戏。</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 繁体中文, 日语, 韩语, 俄语, 土耳其语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 波兰语, 荷兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
